                        <interp inst="t18461214-name-483" type="given" value="FRANCES MATILDA"></interp>FRANCES MATILDA WRIGHT</persName>
                  </hi>. Mr. Ashton lodges with me—my house is undergoing repair—the prisoner worked there—on Tuesday, 24th Nov., he was marbling the fire-place in Mr. Ash ton's room.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
