                        <interp inst="t18461214-name-484" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM SMITH</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable</hi> 220 <hi rend="italic">K.</hi>) The prisoner was given into my custody, on a charge of stealing a scarf—he said he knew nothing about any scarf—he gave his address at No. 13, Jewin-street—I went there, and was shown his room by his grandfather—I showed him a key—he opened a box with it, and I found in it this scarf and collar.</p>
